# Backend Mimarisi

NestJS modular monolith. Controller → Service → Prisma/CryptoService/PolicyScope. HTTP concern controller'da; iş kuralı service'te.

## Modül İskeleti

Her feature module:

| Dosya | Zorunlu |
| --- | --- |
| `*.module.ts` | DI config |
| `*.controller.ts` | HTTP (endpoint varsa) |
| `*.service.ts` | Business logic |
| `dto/` | Request/response DTO |
| `__tests__/` | Unit/slice test |

Modüller arası: (1) `packages/shared|dto|policy` import, (2) NestJS module export (authorization, crypto, audit global), (3) outbox event — **doğrudan cross-module service call yasak**.

## Middleware Zinciri (Sıra Değişmez)

Helmet → CORS (allowlist, wildcard yasak) → CSRF (mutating) → body parser → rate limit → correlation ID → session guard → auth/tracking guard → policy guard → validation pipe → audit interceptor → response transform → exception filter.

Public intake/tracking: session guard exempt. Tracking: `TrackingGuard` (header auth).

## Transaction Pattern

Birden fazla tablo veya outbox → tek `$transaction`:

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — domain + audit aynı transaction
return this.prisma.$transaction(async (tx) => {
  const result = await this.domainOp(tx, command);
  await this.auditPublisher.publish(tx, { eventType: 'CASE_TRANSITION', ... });
  return result;
});

// ✗ Yanlış — audit transaction dışında
await this.domainOp(command);
await this.auditPublisher.publish(...); // fail-closed ihlali
```

## Worker

`apps/worker` ayrı entrypoint; aynı Prisma/service tanımları. Cron: `@nestjs/schedule` — `setInterval` yasak.

## Anti-pattern'ler

- Controller'da Prisma/crypto/policy logic
- Service'te `Request`/`Response` erişimi
- Modül A → Modül B service inject (outbox kullan)
- `prisma migrate dev` production'da

